    doc/UpstreamBugs/Haddock.Debian.txt
    doc/UpstreamBugs/Cabal/Clean.txt doc/UpstreamBugs/Cabal/GHCi.txt
    tests/Tests.hs tests/runTests.sh tests/FileTestInput.gpf tests/tarballs.sh
